oub:modification.regulation.oub:information.text: Commission Delegated Regulation (EU) 2018/172 of 28 November 2017 amending Annexes I and V to Regulation (EU) No 649/2012 of the European Parliament and of the Council concerning the export and import of hazardous chemicals

oub:footnote.description.oub:description: The export of mercury compounds and of the mixtures of mercury subject to Article 3(2) of Regulation (EU) 2017/852 shall be prohibited.

Eligibility to benefit from this preference is subject to the presentation of a proof of origin stating the community origin of the goods, in the context of the agreement between the European Union and the Swiss Confederation.
